Enum BrpDefaultSettlementMessageContent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BrpDefaultSettlementMessageContent>
      • energy.usef.brp.service.business.BrpDefaultSettlementMessageContent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BrpDefaultSettlementMessageContent>

    public enum BrpDefaultSettlementMessageContent
extends Enum<BrpDefaultSettlementMessageContent>
    Enumeration of the default values which can be passed in a dummy settlement message (i.e. when no flex trading occurred during a period but that a settlement message has to be sent nonetheless).
